---
import { Comment } from 'astro-pure/advanced'
import { Button, Collapse, Spoiler, Timeline } from 'astro-pure/user'
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'
import Substats from '@/components/about/Substats.astro'
import ToolSection from '@/components/about/ToolSection.astro'

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'about-me', text: 'Who am I?' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'daily-life', text: 'What do I do daily?' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'personality', text: 'What kind of person am I?' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'why-blog', text: 'Why I blog' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'contact', text: 'Contact me' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'tools', text: 'Tools' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'social-networks', text: 'Social Networks' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'website-history', text: 'Website History' }
]
---

<PageLayout title='About' {headings} info='/about'>
  <!-- Introduction -->
  <p>Student / Gaming Enthusiast / Music Listener</p>
  <p>
    Tsing_loong, a <span class="line-through text-gray-500">key high school student</span> now I'm just a rat.
  </p>
  <Button title='Contact Me' class='w-fit' href='#contact' style='ahead' />

  {/* Who am I? */}
  <h2 id='about-me'>Who am I?</h2>
  <p>
    Tsing_loong, a <span class="line-through text-gray-500">key high school student</span> now I'm just a rat
  </p>

  {/* What do I do daily? */}
  <h2 id='daily-life'>What do I do daily?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Daydreaming</li>
    <li>(Reluctantly) dealing with schoolwork</li>
    <li>Listening to music, mainly instrumental music</li>
    <li>Playing games, including but not limited to:
      <ul class="ml-4 mt-2">
        <li>Minecraft</li>
        <li>Cytus II</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  {/* What kind of person am I? */}
  <h2 id='personality'>What kind of person am I?</h2>
  <ul class="space-y-3">
    <li>
      <strong>Overall:</strong> No exact definition. It's up to the object who is observing me
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h2 id="quotes">Some Lyrics and Sentences</h2>
  <ul class="space-y-3">
    <li>
      寻不到花的折翼枯叶蝶 永远也看不见凋谢 
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（许嵩，《断桥残雪》，2007）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      人间的满也是这人间的空 你可想过你为何匆匆
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（陈鸿宇，《无用清净梦》，2021）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      兰草枯荡 星辰璀璨
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（灵感来自 K-ICM/APJ，《Mr. Lonely - Ai Mang Cô Đơn Đi》，2021）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      You can be just the one you want be
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（Darin Zanyar，《Be What You Wanna Be》，2004）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      生命中最善良的时光 就像是水一样明亮 
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（丢火车乐队，《茶底世界》，2008）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      千里长篷曲终人散尽，留下那红楼一曲唱不休
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（庞龙，《红楼梦》，2011）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      每个人都害怕被 看出内心的脆弱
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">（许嵩，《全球变冷》，2012）</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      下坠的石头以为自由落体运动是遵循自己的意志，奋力向上爬的人们以为自己是命运的主宰 
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        （叶远泊：人生短暂，尽兴而活 - 每日知讯的文章 - 
        <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/314304106" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          知乎
        </a>）
      </span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  {/* Why I blog */}
  <h2 id='why-blog'>Why I blog</h2>
  <p>To record my past self and find comfort in the future.</p>

  {/* Contact me */}
  <h2 id='contact'>Contact me</h2>
  <p>
    QQ: 
    <a href="tencent://AddContact/?fromId=45&fromSubId=1&subcmd=all&uin=2014912641" 
       class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
      2014912641
    </a>
  </p>

  {/* Tools */}
  <h2 id='tools'>Tools</h2>
  <p>Tools and software I commonly use:</p>
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Games'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'Minecraft',
        description: 'Sandbox building game',
        href: 'https://www.minecraft.net/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/minecraft.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Cytus II',
        description: 'Music rhythm game',
        href: 'https://www.rayark.com/g/cytus2/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/cytus.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Learning Tools'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'VS Code',
        description: 'Code editor',
        href: 'https://code.visualstudio.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/vscode.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Chrome',
        description: 'Web browser',
        href: 'https://www.google.com/chrome/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/chrome.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'Typora',
        description: 'Markdown editor',
        href: 'https://typora.io/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/typora.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />
  <ToolSection
    class='mb-5'
    title='Music'
    tools={[
      {
        name: 'NetEase Cloud Music',
        description: 'Music player',
        href: 'https://music.163.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/netease-music.svg?raw')
      },
      {
        name: 'QQ Music',
        description: 'Music player',
        href: 'https://y.qq.com/',
        icon: import('@/assets/tools/qq-music.svg?raw')
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* Social Networks */}
  <h2 id='social-networks'>Social Networks</h2>
  <p>
    You can find my presence on these platforms, feel free to connect.
  </p>
  <Substats
    stats={[
      {
        platform: 'QQ',
        icon: 'rss',
        color: '#12b7f5',
        link: 'tencent://AddContact/?fromId=45&fromSubId=1&subcmd=all&uin=2014912641',
        text: 'QQ',
        api: 'qq/2014912641'
      },
      {
        platform: 'GitHub',
        icon: 'github',
        link: 'https://github.com/tsingloong611',
        text: 'followers',
        api: 'github/tsingloong611'
      },
      {
        platform: 'Steam',
        icon: 'steam',
        color: '#50769d',
        link: 'https://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561199084372866/',
        text: 'games',
        api: 'steamgames/76561199084372866'
      }
    ]}
  />

  {/* Website History */}
  <h2 id='website-history'>Website History</h2>
  <p>The development journey of this blog:</p>
  <Timeline
    events={[
      {
        date: '2021-02-10',
        content: 'Started building personal blog with Hexo, using next theme'
      },
      {
        date: '2021-04',
        content: 'Switched to Butterfly theme'
      },
      {
        date: '2023-10',
        content: 'Site went offline'
      },
      {
        date: '2024-09-28',
        content: 'Reactivated the site'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-06-24',
        content: 'Started migrating from Hexo to <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro</a>, using modern tech stack'
      },
      {
        date: '2025-06-24',
        content: 'Developed remark-hexo-tags plugin to make Astro support Hexo tag syntax'
      }
    ]}
  />
  
  <p>
    The smooth operation and personalized customization of this website also relies on the resources and technical support provided by the following excellent projects/service providers:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Framework & Theme: <a href='https://astro.build/' target='_blank'>Astro</a> + <a
        href='https://github.com/cworld1/astro-theme-pure'
        target='_blank'>Astro Theme Pure</a
      >
    </li>
    <li>
      Website Hosting: <a href='https://github.com/Tsingloong611/tsingloong611.github.io' target='_blank'>Github Pages</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      Hexo Tag Support: <a href='https://github.com/Tsingloong611/remark-hexo-tags' target='_blank'>remark-hexo-tags</a>
    </li>
    <li>Comment System: <a href='https://waline.js.org' target='_blank'>Waline</a></li>
    <li>
      Visit Statistics: <a href='https://github.com/spencerwooo/substats' target='_blank'
        >Substats</a
      >
    </li>
  </ul>
  
  <!-- Hidden developer comments -->
  <!-- Building a blog on GitHub for free is nice, but the lag is quite annoying, though I'm content with it. -->
  <!-- 2021.4.3 20.05 2022年1月30日 22:33:14 -->
  
  <Comment slot='bottom' />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Strikethrough style */
  .line-through {
    text-decoration: line-through;
    text-decoration-color: #ef4444;
  }
  
  /* Lyrics quote style */
  .text-sm {
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  
  /* List style */
  ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .space-y-3 > li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>